  "title": "QUANTITY SURVEYOR",
  "description": "<p>Job Description / Responsibilities:-<br /></p><p>a. Preparing and taking off quantities from drawing and tender documents;<br /></p><p>b. Request quotation from subcontractors / suppliers and compare pricing for consolidation;<br /></p><p>c. Prepare, maintain and manage tender documents that comprises of BOQ, tender clarifications and etc;<br /></p><p>d. Tender submission, handle progressive claims / payments, variation orders and finalized project account;<br /></p><p>Requirement:-<br /></p><p>a. Min 3 years QS related working experience or Building related working experience;<br /></p><p>b. Team player and able to work independently;<br /></p><p>c. Strong interpersonal skills and possesses good working attitude;<br /></p><p>d. Highly responsible, reliable, ability to work under pressure in a fast-paced environment;<br /></p>",
